-scaled.jpg 1801w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-3-728x889.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-3-768x938.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-3-1257x1536.jpg 1257w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-3-1676x2048.jpg 1676w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-3-150x183.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1801px) 100vw, 1801px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201801%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-3-scaled.jpg 1801w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-3-728x889.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-3-768x938.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-3-1257x1536.jpg 1257w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-3-1676x2048.jpg 1676w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-3-150x183.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-3-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMy previous 20-something self would be horrible by all of that, but oh my, I LOVE IT.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnyway. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThere is something about the grilled chicken + broccoli combo that is just SO good. It’s fresh and light tasting while also having this comforting feeling all at the same time.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWell, maybe it’s the cheese. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScratch that, it’s definitely the cheese. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnd the garlic sauce!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-4-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"grilled chicken broccoli puff pastry pizza\" width=\"1665\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-pizza/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Garlicky Grilled Chicken and Broccoli Puff Pastry Pizza.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-4-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-4-scaled.jpg 1665w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-4-728x962.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-4-768x1015.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-4-1162x1536.jpg 1162w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-4-1550x2048.jpg 1550w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-4-150x198.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1665px) 100vw, 1665px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201665%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-4-scaled.jpg 1665w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-4-728x962.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-4-768x1015.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-4-1162x1536.jpg 1162w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-4-1550x2048.jpg 1550w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-4-150x198.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-4-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis whole meal starts by making some super garlickly olive oil with crushed red pepper. It is SO good. It will elevate anything. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnd for some reason, I always choose to have it with broccoli. It usually makes an appearance in \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2020/04/garlic-sauce-pasta/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003emy shrimp and broccoli bucatini\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e. But believe me when I say, it works anywhere. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt’s not spicy or TOO garlicky because the garlic toasts slowly in the olive oil. It reminds me of roasted garlic where there is even some sweetness. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-5-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"grilled chicken broccoli puff pastry pizza\" width=\"1720\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-pizza/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Garlicky Grilled Chicken and Broccoli Puff Pastry Pizza.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-5-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-5-scaled.jpg 1720w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-5-728x931.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-5-768x982.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-5-1201x1536.jpg 1201w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-5-1601x2048.jpg 1601w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-5-150x192.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1720px) 100vw, 1720px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201720%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-5-scaled.jpg 1720w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-5-728x931.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-5-768x982.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-5-1201x1536.jpg 1201w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-5-1601x2048.jpg 1601w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-5-150x192.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-5-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAs usual, I’m throwing this pizza on some puff pastry because, oh gosh, why not? I love it so much, it’s easy to use and very accessible. This is my monthly reminder that I really enjoy the puff pastry that is not frozen, but comes refrigerated near the pie crusts. And it comes in one big sheet – not perforated at all. \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"more-97951\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-8-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"grilled chicken broccoli puff pastry pizza\" width=\"1717\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-pizza/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Garlicky Grilled Chicken and Broccoli Puff Pastry Pizza.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-8-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-8-scaled.jpg 1717w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-8-728x933.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-8-768x984.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-8-1199x1536.jpg 1199w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-8-1599x2048.jpg 1599w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-8-150x192.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1717px) 100vw, 1717px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201717%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-8-scaled.jpg 1717w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-8-728x933.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-8-768x984.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-8-1199x1536.jpg 1199w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-8-1599x2048.jpg 1599w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-8-150x192.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-8-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe only secret I have for puff pastry pizza is not to overload it. Keep the toppings evenly distributed and don’t make things too heavy on the crust. Spread the heavier toppings (chicken, broccoli) out over the whole sheet and you should be good. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-7-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"grilled chicken broccoli puff pastry pizza\" width=\"1697\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-pizza/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Garlicky Grilled Chicken and Broccoli Puff Pastry Pizza.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-7-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-7-scaled.jpg 1697w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-7-728x944.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-7-768x996.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-7-1185x1536.jpg 1185w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-7-1580x2048.jpg 1580w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-7-150x194.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1697px) 100vw, 1697px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201697%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-7-scaled.jpg 1697w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-7-728x944.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-7-768x996.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-7-1185x1536.jpg 1185w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-7-1580x2048.jpg 1580w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-7-150x194.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pastry-pizza-7-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBake this baby and it’s so flaky and crisp and wonderful. It’s also a lovely little appetizer or snack. Serve it with a big greens salad for dinner. FRIYAY. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/grilled-chicken-broccoli-puff-pas